{"tid":733559,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Harry Maguire 高材生變晉級功臣","createTime":"2018-07-08T00:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T01:42:22.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c47fdd3c4a97e580902a53f13f447b3402dfaa4","tid":733559,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T00:17:06.000Z","msg":"常說「頭大無腦」，以一記頭槌助英格蘭殺入4強的「大頭仔」哈利馬古尼（Harry Maguire），卻比很多人聰明。<br />\n<br />\n這名25歲中堅，又是打破另一迷思的好例子：頭槌頂壞腦。<br />\n<br />\n中學考GCSE會考，馬古尼拿的是A*和A成績，據指數學頭腦相當不俗，若然當初沒有決定走上職業足球路，今日很可能是一名商界精英。讀書聰明，馬古尼沒有「走精面」，而是一步一步努力改進，慢慢走上今時今日的位置。<br />\n<br />\n2014年他仍在甲組（英格蘭第三級別聯賽）為錫菲聯比賽，之後轉投侯城，球隊去年降班才以1700萬鎊加盟李斯特城，續留英超兩年前，馬古尼已去過法國「參與」歐國盃，但身份只是普通球迷，與友人齊齊為英格蘭打氣；短短兩年後，他終於真正以球員身份出戰世界盃，更在8強比賽裏入波──他全場總共9次爭贏頭槌、6次成功解圍、觸球68次，傳送成功率亦達85%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wc2018.hk01.com/article/208015/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E5%85%A54%E5%BC%B7%E5%8A%9F%E8%87%A3-%E8%AA%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9?utm_source=fbpost+sports&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=WorldCup2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwc2018.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F208015%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259B%2583-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%2585%25A54%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2587%25A3-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%3Futm_source%3Dfbpost%2Bsports%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_campaign%3DWorldCup2018&d=lVNrecP%2FT6exM8alYbDMijACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=24242ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wc2018.hk01.com/article/208015/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%E5%85%A54%E5%BC%B7%E5%8A%9F%E8%87%A3-%E8%AA%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9?utm_source=fbpost+sports&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=WorldCup2018</a>"},{"pid":"14dc1a89b7d550bb4c3759d887b395e4163565bc","tid":733559,"uid":85926,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"cite